The corpses of a man, one Ifeanyi Nwokwu and his alleged concubine, Mrs Nkechi Ezaka Ucha were on Monday night discovered in Umuezeoka Umueze Ezza Effium in Ohaukwu LGA of Ebonyi state. The woman is said to be a widow while the man has a wife. They were said to have been having an affair. Neighbours discovered their corpses in the man’s house after they mounted a search for them, having not seen them for a while. They were believed to have been murdered by unknown persons. Police spokesman confirmed the deaths. She said the Police have launched an investigation to unravel what led to their death. Details soon… 